{"title":"Infección de Clostridioides difficile-2024-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Infectología/Infección de Clostridioides difficile-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Infección de\\NClostridioides difficile","guid":"Owi0rwT3n5wguI5-ZG7mTA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"C. difficile\\N(Clostridioides\\Ndifficile)","guid":"Bzczyn28LgOMnq9VFLeXTw","children":[]},{"id":"2","parent":"0","text":"Gram(+), bacilo → diarrea\\Nasociada a uso de ATB\\N(Clostridioides infection, CDI).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"0","text":"Factores de riesgo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"• Pacientes hospitalizados ↔\\Nresidentes en LTC (long-term care)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"3","text":"• Transmisión: esporas difíciles de\\Nerradicar (vía fecal-oral)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"3","text":"• Uso previo de ATB → alteración flora\\Nintestinal → infección por C. difficile","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"Presentación clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"• Diarrea + fiebre\\N+ dolor abd","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"• CDI severo/fulminante → íleo\\Nparalítico, megacolon tóxico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"• Colonización\\Nasintomática en la\\Nmayoría","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• Test de heces (toxinas o\\Ncepas toxigénicas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"• Colitis pseudomembranosa\\Nen imagen/endoscopía","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"• 1ra línea:\\NVancomicina,\\NFidaxomicina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"• Prevención: aislamiento, cohortes de\\Npacientes, higiene estricta","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación CDI:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"1. CDI nosocomial: Dx en paciente con\\Natención intrahospitalaria ≤12 sem","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"2. CDI comunitario: Dx sin atención\\Nintrahospitalaria ≤12 sem","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"3. CDI recurrente: Recurrencia de\\Nsíntomas + test (+) (NAAT o EIA) tras\\Nepisodio confirmado ≤8 sem","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"Referencias: (1).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología de CDI:","guid":"mRgOMx3eAtRHv8tpdTnQJg","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"• Incidencia: ∼220,000 casos en\\Nhospitalizados/anual + ∼13,000\\Nmuertes/anual en EE. UU. (4)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"• CDI nosocomial: Más\\Ncomún >65 años (5)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"• CDI comunitario: Afecta típicamente\\Na individuos ∼50 años (6)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"0","text":"Etiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• Patógeno:\\NClostridioides\\Ndifficile","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"• Gram(+) bacilo,\\Nanaerobio obligado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"• Cepas\\Ntoxigénicas →\\NCDI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"26","text":"• Forman esporas\\Nresistentes (calor, ATB,\\Nácido)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"26","text":"• Germinación →\\Nbacilos funcionales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"26","text":"• Muy contagioso,\\Ntransmisión fecal-oral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"26","text":"• CDI comunitario:\\Nvía fecal-oral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"26","text":"• CDI nosocomial:\\Nsuperficies/eq. médico\\Ncontaminado","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"0","text":"Factores de\\Nriesgo para CDI:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"1. ATB recientes (7,8)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"• ATB de alto riesgo (OR ≥ 5):\\NClindamicina, Cefalosporinas,\\NFluoroquinolonas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"• ATB de riesgo moderado (OR\\N1-5): Penicilina, Macrólidos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"35","text":"2. Edad avanzada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"35","text":"3. Supresión ácido gástrico (IBP) o\\Nbypass (alimentación enteral)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"35","text":"4. Hospitalización\\Nreciente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"35","text":"5. Enfermedades graves","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"35","text":"6. Inmunosupresión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"35","text":"7. EII (Enfermedad\\Ninflamatoria intestinal) (9)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"0","text":"Referencias: [1][2][3].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología de CDI:","guid":"CCirGGDjJLh9wXuP4l1UlA","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"• Factores de virulencia\\Nprincipales: Toxinas A y B (10,11)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"0","text":"Toxina A\\N(Enterotoxina):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"• Estructura:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"• Sitio activo:\\Ndominio N-terminal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"• Dominio central:\\Nhidrofóbico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"48","text":"• Sitio de unión:\\Ndominio C-terminal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"48","text":"• Mecanismo de acción:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"48","text":"1. Unión a borde en\\Ncepillo de enterocitos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"48","text":"2. Endocitosis\\Nmediada por receptor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"48","text":"3. Cambio conformacional →\\Nexposición del dominio activo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"48","text":"4. Glucosilación de proteínas\\Nblanco (Rac, Cdc42, RhoA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"48","text":"5. Disrupción del\\Ncitoesqueleto de actina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"48","text":"6. ↑ Permeabilidad epitelial +\\Napoptosis → diarrea","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"0","text":"Toxina B (Citotoxina):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"• Estructura:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"• Sitio de unión:\\Ndominio C-terminal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"• Dominio de\\Ntranslocación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"• Dominio con\\Nproteasa de cisteína","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"60","text":"• Dominio catalítico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"60","text":"• Mecanismo de acción:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"60","text":"• Igual que toxina A","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"60","text":"• Además: formación de poros en membrana\\Nendosomal → liberación de contenido endosomal\\Nal citosol → efecto citopático","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"0","text":"Referencias: [1][2][3].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"0","text":"Características\\Nclínicas de CDI:","guid":"zY-wndAihl7omMnt-pphUw","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"• Inicio de síntomas: Durante tratamiento\\Ncon ATB o 2-10 días post-inicio.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"• 25-40% → manifestación tardía (hasta\\N10 semanas post-tratamiento)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"0","text":"Síntomas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"1. Diarrea\\Nacuosa\\N(CDAD):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"• ≥3 deposiciones/día +\\Nolor característico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"• Puede contener moco\\No sangre oculta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"73","text":"• Raro:\\Nhematoquecia y\\Nmelena","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"73","text":"2. Dolor abdominal cólico,\\Nnáuseas, anorexia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"73","text":"3. Sensibilidad abdominal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"73","text":"4. Fiebre +\\Ndeshidratación (↑\\Ngravedad)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"73","text":"5. CDI fulminante:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"73","text":"• Distensión abdominal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"73","text":"• Hipovolemia severa\\N(megacolon tóxico, íleo\\Nparalítico)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"0","text":"Referencias: [1][2][3].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico de CDI:","guid":"gKN-3Fo_oeqBS2hGSXHsjg","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"• Basado en síntomas clínicos típicos\\N(en pacientes con factores de riesgo) y\\Nuno de los siguientes:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"1. Toxinas o cepas toxigénicas\\Nde C. difficile en heces","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"2. Colitis pseudomembranosa confirmada\\Npor endoscopía o histopatología","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"0","text":"Manejo inicial:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"• Iniciar medidas de\\Nprevención/control de la\\Ninfección.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"0","text":"Pacientes con diarrea:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"1. Considerar otras\\Netiologías de diarrea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"2. Sospechar CDI en diarrea de\\Ninicio reciente sin explicación +\\Nfactores de riesgo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"3. Pruebas iniciales: análisis de\\Nheces para toxinas y cepas\\Ntoxigénicas de C. difficile","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"0","text":"Pacientes con íleo\\Nsospechoso de CDI:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"• Considerar PCR de\\Nhisopados rectales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"0","text":"Imágenes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"• Útil en dolor abdominal no diferenciado o\\Nsospecha de complicaciones","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"0","text":"Endoscopía:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"• Si el Dx no es claro tras\\Npruebas iniciales o insuficiente\\Nrespuesta a ATB empíricos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"0","text":"Evaluar\\Ngravedad de\\NCDI:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"• Iniciar tratamiento ATB\\Nempírico si CDI fulminante","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"0","text":"Consultar a\\Ngastroenterología/enfermedades\\Ninfecciosas si el Dx es\\Nincierto.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"0","text":"Referencias: [1][2][3].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"0","text":"Estudios de laboratorio\\Nrutinarios en CDI:","guid":"UovCDzbU7eKZrhk75WFZ6w","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"• Resultados\\Ninespecíficos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"1. CBC:\\NLeucocitosis (1,\\N2)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"2. BMP:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"105","text":"• ↑ Creatinina sérica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"105","text":"• Desequilibrio\\Nelectrolítico\\N(hipokalemia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"105","text":"• ↓ Albúmina sérica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"105","text":"3. Gases sanguíneos\\N(arteriales/venosos):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"105","text":"• ↑ Lactato","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"105","text":"• Acidosis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"0","text":"Pruebas de heces para toxinas y cepas\\Ntoxigénicas de C. difficile:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"0","text":"Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"• Adultos: Heces líquidas ≥3\\Nveces/24h, sin explicación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"116","text":"• Niños: Considerar en diarrea\\Nprolongada o en empeoramiento +\\Nfactores de riesgo para CDI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"0","text":"Modalidades:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"1. Alta sensibilidad:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"• EIA para antígeno GDH (glutamato\\Ndeshidrogenasa de C. difficile)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"119","text":"• NAAT (p.ej., PCR) para\\Ntoxinas de C. difficile","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"119","text":"2. Alta especificidad:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"119","text":"• EIA para toxinas A y\\NB de C. difficile","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"119","text":"3. Otras pruebas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"119","text":"• CCNA: Ensayo de\\Nneutralización de citotoxicidad\\N(detecta toxina en heces)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"119","text":"• Cultivo de cepas\\Ntoxigénicas de C. difficile","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"0","text":"Estrategia de\\Npruebas sugerida:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"• Enfoque algorítmico multi-test\\Nbasado en la probabilidad\\Npretest (PTP) de CDI:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"1. Prueba inicial: Alta sensibilidad\\N(NAAT o EIA para GDH)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"128","text":"• NAAT o EIA negativo para\\NGDH: CDI descartado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"128","text":"• NAAT o EIA positivo para GDH: Confirmar\\NCDI con prueba de alta especificidad (EIA\\Npara toxinas de C. difficile)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"128","text":"• EIA positivo para\\Ntoxinas: Dx confirmado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"128","text":"• EIA negativo\\Npara toxinas:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"128","text":"• Alta PTP: Considerar NAAT si no se\\Nrealizó como prueba inicial.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"128","text":"• Iniciar ATB\\Nempíricos para\\NCDI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"128","text":"• Baja/moderada PTP:\\NConsiderar Dx alternativo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"0","text":"Recomendaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"• No repetir pruebas dentro\\Nde 7 días de diarrea.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"• No realizar pruebas en\\Nindividuos asintomáticos.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"0","text":"Referencias: [1][2][3].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos\\Nadicionales para\\NCDI:","guid":"EIA1GwH4Xt0srVp4j6OsrQ","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"0","text":"Imágenes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"• Indicaciones (no\\Nrutinarias para Dx de CDI):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"1. Sospecha de\\Ncomplicaciones (perforación\\Nintestinal, megacolon tóxico,\\Níleo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"2. Evaluar\\Nseveridad de\\NCDI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"143","text":"3. Evaluación inicial del dolor abdominal\\Nno diferenciado o distensión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"143","text":"• Modalidades:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"143","text":"• Rx abdomen o TC abdomen\\N(con contraste IV/VO)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"143","text":"• Hallazgos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"143","text":"1. Colitis\\Npseudomembranosa:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"143","text":"• Engrosamiento de la pared\\Ncolónica (signo más común)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"143","text":"• Signo del acordeón (TC con\\Ncontraste): áreas alternadas de\\Nbaja y alta atenuación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"143","text":"• Nodularidad de la\\Npared colónica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"143","text":"• Estriación pericolónica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"143","text":"• Ascitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"143","text":"2. Complicaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"143","text":"• Perforación intestinal: aire\\Nintraperitoneal libre","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"143","text":"• Megacolon tóxico: dilatación del colon (>6\\Ncm) + pérdida de haustración","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"143","text":"• Íleo paralítico: dilatación de\\Nintestino delgado y grueso sin\\Nobstrucción mecánica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"161","parent":"0","text":"Endoscopía:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"162","parent":"161","text":"• Indicaciones\\N(no rutinarias):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"161","text":"1. Si el Dx no es claro\\Ntras pruebas iniciales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"161","text":"2. Alta probabilidad pretest (PTP) y\\Nrespuesta insuficiente a ATB empíricos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"161","text":"• Modalidades:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"161","text":"• Colonoscopía o\\Nsigmoidoscopía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"161","text":"• Hallazgos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"161","text":"1. Mucosa normal o\\Neritematosa y friable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"161","text":"2. Colitis\\Npseudomembranosa:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"161","text":"• Placas amarillo-blancas\\Nelevadas → pseudomembranas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"161","text":"• Lesiones solitarias o\\Ndifusas en casos graves","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación de\\Nseveridad de CDI:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"1. CDI no severo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"172","text":"• Leucocitos\\N<15,000/mm³","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"172","text":"• Creatinina\\Nsérica <1.5 mg/dL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"172","text":"2. CDI severo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"172","text":"• Leucocitos\\N≥15,000/mm³","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"172","text":"• Creatinina\\Nsérica ≥1.5 mg/dL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"172","text":"3. CDI fulminante:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"172","text":"• Criterios de CDI severo + hipotensión,\\Nshock, íleo o megacolon tóxico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento\\Nantibiótico para\\NCDI:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"• CDI no severo/severo:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"1. Primera línea: Fidaxomicina\\NVO o Vancomicina VO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"181","text":"2. Segunda línea (casos no severos):\\NMetronidazol VO (si Fidaxomicina o\\NVancomicina no disponibles)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"181","text":"• CDI fulminante:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"181","text":"1. Primera línea:\\NVancomicina VO (dosis\\Nalta)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"181","text":"2. Añadir Metronidazol IV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"181","text":"3. Si hay íleo paralítico, considerar\\Nenemas de Vancomicina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"181","text":"• CDI recurrente:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"181","text":"• Primera recurrencia:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"181","text":"1. Fidaxomicina VO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"181","text":"2. Vancomicina VO en esquema\\Nde reducción y pulsos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"181","text":"• Recurrencias\\Nsubsiguientes:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"181","text":"1. Fidaxomicina VO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"181","text":"2. Vancomicina VO\\Nseguida de Rifamixina VO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"181","text":"3. Esquema de reducción y\\Npulsos con Vancomicina","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"0","text":"Referencias: [1][2][3].","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"0","text":"Trasplante de\\Nmicrobiota fecal\\N(FMT):","guid":"N4OaKmf21ISgeEucu5WxhA","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"• Donación de heces (vía cápsulas,\\Ncolonoscopía o enema)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"198","text":"1. CDI severo o fulminante sin\\Nmejora tras 48-72h de terapia\\Nmédica máxima (2,16)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"198","text":"2. Pacientes adultos/pediátricos\\Ncon ≥2 recurrencias pese a terapia\\NATB adecuada (1,2)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"203","parent":"0","text":"Manejo quirúrgico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"203","text":"• Pacientes críticos con CDI\\Nsevero/fulminante refractario a\\NATB, especialmente si hay:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"203","text":"1. Leucocitosis severa\\No lactato elevado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"203","text":"2. Complicaciones (megacolon tóxico,\\Nisquemia, perforación intestinal)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"203","text":"• Procedimientos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"203","text":"1. Colectomía total con ileostomía\\Nterminal y muñón rectal grapado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"203","text":"2. Ileostomía en asa con lavado\\Ncolónico seguido de administración\\Nintraluminal de Vancomicina","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"211","parent":"0","text":"Complicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"• Megacolon tóxico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"211","text":"• Íleo paralítico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"211","text":"• Peritonitis, perforación,\\Nformación de abscesos, sepsis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"215","parent":"0","text":"Prevención\\Nprimaria de CDI:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"• Uso prudente de ATB +\\Nprogramas de manejo de ATB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"215","text":"• Insuficiente evidencia para\\Nrecomendar suspender IBP o uso de\\Nprobióticos para prevención","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"218","parent":"0","text":"Prevención\\Nsecundaria de CDI\\N(1):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"219","parent":"218","text":"1. Aislamiento: Habitación individual con\\Nbaño designado o cohortes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"218","text":"2. Equipo de protección:\\NGuantes + bata protectora,\\Ncambiar entre pacientes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"218","text":"3. Higiene de manos: Lavar con\\Nagua y jabón, no usar\\Ndesinfectantes alcohólicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"218","text":"4. Desinfección de superficies: Con\\Nagentes esporicidas (p.ej., peróxido de\\Nhidrógeno, hipoclorito de sodio)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"218","text":"5. Equipo médico: Desechable o\\Ndedicado, esterilización adecuada con\\Nautoclave si es necesario","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"224","parent":"0","text":"Grupos especiales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"• C. difficile en infantes:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"224","text":"• Mayoría\\Ncolonizados\\Nasintomáticos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"224","text":"• Factores de riesgo: Prematuridad,\\Nanomalías anatómicas (enf. de\\NHirschsprung, malrotación intestinal)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"224","text":"• Tratamiento: Vancomicina\\NVO o Metronidazol VO","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"0","text":"Lista de manejo agudo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"1. Iniciar aislamiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"229","text":"2. Suspender ATB\\Nprecipitantes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"229","text":"3. Revisar CBC, BMP y\\Nevaluar severidad de CDI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"229","text":"4. Corregir desequilibrios\\Nhidroelectrolíticos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"229","text":"5. Pruebas de heces para CDI o PCR de\\Nhisopado rectal (en íleo paralítico)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"229","text":"6. Considerar imágenes\\N(complicaciones: íleo,\\Nmegacolon tóxico, perforación)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"229","text":"7. ATB para CDI o ATB\\Nempíricos para CDI fulminante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"229","text":"8. Consultas urgentes\\N(gastro/infecciones/surgery/ICU en casos\\Nseveros)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"238","parent":"0","text":"Referencias: [1][2][3].","guid":"","children":[]}]},"node_count":238,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Infectología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Infectología","filename":"Infección de Clostridioides difficile-2024-1","id":"map_1149","resolved_references":[]}